beer.beer_description:
Smoked Chilli Stout With Salted Caramel
Burn baby burn - ya nostrils out! We've taken hot jalapenos and smoked 'em over flamin' Irish whiskey barrel oak then added them into a salted caramel stout for the ultimate autumn warmer!
